{"tid":1490763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次虐老擺明唔係比我地睇","createTime":"2019-08-20T07:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:07:36.000Z","uid":261544,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a9b5206fdd68861e547932af207bc57ea6cdc1","tid":1490763,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:58:09.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下，成兩個月<br />\nHA而家先畀呢段片我哋，<br />\n用意何在?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係想得罪人，但係事實，<br />\n連100萬，200萬，170萬都叫唔郁班高官，成班HA護士罷工，集會，HA都唔回應<br />\n唔通一個立法會議員同家屬投訴幾下就追到丫? <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n佢今次係擺到明畀外國政府睇，<br />\n搵兩件蛋散祭旗，證明佢哋班犬係公平公正公開啦</span></span><br />\n同埋係到集中某一項訴求，等我地分心<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n1. 我地要將成件事嘅觀點帶返去被拘捕嘅義士個到，帶出<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然有cctv同在醫院都咁，更何況在9屋?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 將呢件事帶去國際層面，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">直接指出班犬虐老係違反基本人權，更何況係對著一個手腳均被綁的60歲老人家</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求各國馬上以國家安全為理由，慎重審查所有任職警務人員入境資格及居留權</span></span>,因為point 2"},{"pid":"777961442ce3127ba507d6fc23278496e85bf998","tid":1490763,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:58:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"44faa109df6ad0ad9c770b91107526bdd365cbb0","tid":1490763,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:58:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9cb75367ad2b45da8e3ed0f8d13e366b88b63bf5","tid":1490763,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:58:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"85f3de8d62c83889acab4e7bd6f74c458893a5a6","tid":1490763,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eca43f1b4083f4263cc72ec190ba9db219c88de8","tid":1490763,"uid":261544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-